Release 0.8
===========

+ Added clipping so we don't draw characters that aren't on screen.

+ Adjusted camera angles.

+ Made camera code and drawing code more declarative.  No longer deal with GlMat calls directly.  In case I ever want to try to port to F#/DirectX.

Release 0.7.2
=============

+ OpenArena graphics and models included by default.

+ glut library included.

+ Improved camera angles.

Release 0.6
===========

+ Faster graphics rendering.

+ Can now act as a front end for gnuchess.
